《決勝時刻：戰爭世界》获得了总体积极的评价。据Metacritic统计，Xbox 360版游戏获得了84%的平均分，而PlayStation 3版本则获得了85%的平均分。<ref name="codwawps3rev-metac">{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/games/platforms/ps3/callofdutyworldatwar|title=Call of Duty: World at War (PS3) Review|publisher=Metacritic|accessdate=2008-11-12|archive-date=2010-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100519145655/http://www.metacritic.com/games/platforms/ps3/callofdutyworldatwar|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="codwaw360rev-metac">{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/games/platforms/xbox360/callofdutyworldatwar|title=Call of Duty: World at War (X360) Review|publisher=Metacritic|accessdate=2008-11-12|archive-date=2010-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100220015124/http://www.metacritic.com/games/platforms/xbox360/callofdutyworldatwar|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="codwawpcrev-metac">{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/games/platforms/pc/callofdutyworldatwar|title=Call of Duty: World at War (PC) Review|publisher=Metacritic|accessdate=2008-11-12|archive-date=2010-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100421170523/http://www.metacritic.com/games/platforms/pc/callofdutyworldatwar|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[IGN|IGN]]认为[[Treyarch|Treyarch]]将太平洋战场搬上游戏舞台是正确的选择，但是也指出游戏不断地在时间和空间上跳换，影响了剧情的流畅感。同时，IGN赞扬新引入的co-op模式增加了游戏的耐玩度，而多人游戏部分则是一如既往地好。<ref name="codwawx360rev-ign">{{cite web |url=http://xbox360.ign.com/articles/927/927055p1.html |title=Call of Duty: World at War Review |date=2008-11-11 |accessdate=2008-11-11 |last=Ocampo |first=Jason |publisher=IGN |archive-date=2012-05-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120516194024/http://xbox360.ign.com/articles/927/927055p1.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

Xbox官方杂志的批评焦点是游戏的创新性。尽管为游戏亮出了“play-it-safe sequel”（不差的续作）标志，但仍然强调《戰爭世界》相对《[[決勝時刻4：現代戰爭|決勝時刻4：現代戰爭]]》没有什么提高。此外，评论员认为游戏的单人模式不够精彩，特别是兼顾欧洲战场和太平洋战场，导致游戏在两地的设定都不具备丰富的内涵。评论员形容《战争世界》“更像是使命召唤系列的一款资料片，而不是独立作品”。<ref name="codwawrev-oxm">{{cite web |url=http://oxmonline.com/article/reviews/xbox-360/a-f/call-duty-world-war |title=Call of Duty: World at War Review at OXM |date=2008-11-12 |accessdate=2008-11-13 |last=McCaffrey |first=Ryan |publisher=Official Xbox Magazine |archive-date=2011-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110822154604/http://www.oxmonline.com/article/reviews/xbox-360/a-f/call-duty-world-war |dead-url=no }}</ref>

[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]认为游戏很好地渲染出了战争阴暗、可怕的一面，使得游戏情节格外生动、扣人心弦，但指出二战题材仍然难免俗套。评论员称赞了Sgt. Roebuck、Sgt. Reznov的配音，以及紧张的单人游戏和合作游戏。评论员总结道，回归二战题材的《戰爭世界》是一款不错的游戏，但缺少突破，闪光点不足。<ref name="codwawrev-gspot" />

[[1UP.com|1UP]]认为增加血腥度是游戏的亮点之一，战场上的残肢断臂对渲染战场气氛的悲壮起到很大的作用。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.1up.com/do/reviewPage?cId=3171247&p=1|title=Call of Duty 5 World at War (PC)|publisher=[[1UP.com|1UP.com]]|date=2008-11-21|accessdate=2009-01-01}} (emphasis in original)</ref>

