=== 销售数据 ===
在美国，游戏是2008年11月的销量亚军，共售出141万份。<ref>{{cite news |first=Grace |last=Chng |coauthors=Tan Chong Yaw |title=Video games sales rise in U.S. |work=Digital Life |publisher=[[Singapore_Press_Holdings|Singapore Press Holdings]] |location=Singapore |page=4 |date=17 December 2008 |accessdate=17 December 2008 }}</ref>12月，游戏的[[Xbox_360|Xbox 360]]版和[[PlayStation_3|PlayStation 3]]版则分别是销售亚军和第9名，总共销售133万套。<ref name="gamedaily">{{cite web|title=NPD: Nintendo Drives '08 Industry Sales Past $21 Billion |url=http://www.gamedaily.com/articles/news/npd-nintendo-drives-08-industry-sales-past-21-billion-/?biz=1 |publisher=[[Game_Daily|Game Daily]] |accessdate=2009-01-15 |date=2009-01-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090117013042/http://www.gamedaily.com/articles/news/npd-nintendo-drives-08-industry-sales-past-21-billion-/?biz=1 |archivedate=2009-01-17 }}</ref>[[Wii|Wii]]版则在所有Wii游戏中排在2008年12月榜单的第7名。<ref name="wired">{{cite web |title=Top 10 Games of December 2008, By Platform |url=http://blog.wired.com/games/2009/01/top-10-games-of.html |publisher=blog.[[Wired_News|Wired]].com |accessdate=2009-01-19 |date=2009-01-18 |archive-date=2011-08-17 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/610xGveKe?url=http://www.wired.com/gamelife/2009/01/top-10-games-of/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

在英国，游戏也获得了不俗的成绩。游戏的第一周销量是《使命召唤4：现代战争》当时的两倍。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.totalvideogames.com/Call-of-Duty-World-at-War/news/World-At-War-Doubles-CoD4s-Sales-13446.html|title=World At War Doubles CoD4's Sales News|date=2008-11-18|publisher=Total Video Games|accessdate=2009-02-19|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110717080118/http://www.totalvideogames.com/Call-of-Duty-World-at-War/news/World-At-War-Doubles-CoD4s-Sales-13446.html|archivedate=2011-07-17}}</ref>销售速度则排在所有游戏中的第三名，仅次于两款《[[俠盜獵車手|俠盜獵車手]]》游戏。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.computerandvideogames.com/article.php?id=201950|title=CoD: WaW the third fastest selling game ever|date=2008-11-18|publisher=[[Computer_and_Video_Games|Computer and Video Games]]|accessdate=2009-02-19|archive-date=2009-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090501065140/http://www.computerandvideogames.com/article.php?id=201950|dead-url=no}}</ref>

